[[File:HK_Wan_Chai_MTR_Station_Mrs_Fields_Cookies_1.JPG|thumb]]
'''菲爾斯餅乾'''（{{lang-en|Mrs. Fields}}）是美國一間[[加盟連鎖|加盟連鎖]]餅乾店經營者，主要以費爾茲和[[TCBY|TCBY]]做為核心品牌<ref>{{cite news|title=Mrs. Fields Famous Brands, LLC, Mrs. Fields Financing Company, Inc., and Certain Guarantors: No Action, Interpretive and/or Exemptive Letter of March 24, 2005|publisher=Trust Indenture Act|date=2005-03-24|url=https://www.sec.gov/divisions/corpfin/cf-noaction/fields032405.htm|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/https://www.sec.gov/divisions/corpfin/cf-noaction/fields032405.htm|archivedate=2006-02-28|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

